title: My Voice Memos | it's okay to be sad
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
itunes:subtitle: it's ok to not be ok
itunes:summary:
Today, I went and got lost with my dog in the woods. I think sometimes we all need a break from reality and this is where I find mine. I actually do a lot of thinking when I come out here. I decided to record a voice memo about all the thoughts I had while out here and this is what came to mind ...
